	   <tr><td colspan=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;1st lets clarify why people play pal. 1st is that some people may have played them in a d&d type setting where they where more than clerics w/ swords. 2nd the idea of a holy warrior is appealing to a great % of us. <br>  Now this is my OPINION (not law) on Pal. on everquest. The class needs duel wield (bards have it!!) OR the ability to bezerk ANS make crit. hits. All three of these would be ridiculus but if Verant wants to cater to thier customers needs either my 1st or my second option is mandatory. Then this would put a pal. in form of what they should be. If warriors b*tch and whine....heres some cheese! Pal lvl slower anyway.<br>  Next piont: Pal. need more equip options. Take a look at the lists availible and you will find about 10% or less of the decent equip usable by Pal. Now this would be o.k. if in fact Pal. where blessed by thier gods w/ abilities to save better, immune to disease/mind effects/could turn undead . But they cant. Basically verant needs to address this class.<br>            From Gromble...7th Hammer<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
