	   <tr><td colspan=2>Duel Wield - NO. I've said this several times. Give me a Holy 1-Hander and a Shield, or a Big-Ass-Holy 2-Hander all the way. We are not Warriors and Duel Wield would make Warriors obscelete.<br><br>Pets - Only if Verant brings in Horses and I don't see them doing that ever.<br><br>Criticals - I like the idea of criticals. Maybe at higher levels or maybe never as good as Warriors, but we should get them.<br><br>Better Saves - I REALLY like this idea. I can't believe I never thought of it before, but we should have some better Saves since we are supposed to be blessed by our gods. Sks get pets since their evil gods assign them a minion, we should get better Saves.<br><br>Equipment Options - The real simple solution here is to make Ro Armour a little easier to get. We have to go into one of the nastier zones with one of the highest rates of trains to get supplies for EVERY piece of our Armour. I still have yet to see a Pally with Ro (I know they're out there, I just haven't seen one yet).<br><br>&nbsp;<br>________<br><br>I've travelled this world and have seen many wondrous things. You are not one of them.</td></tr>
